{
  "stem": "1062.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[GERMAN] You know, a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So everybody ran away, because the Jews were like, you know, like, like, a [NON-ENGLISH], like, like, like, like a plague was coming.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So everybody-- you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were all inside the-- inside the houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I saw children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I saw civilians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So it brought me back a little memories, you know, from, from, from civilian life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We went to Katowice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then we came into a town called Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Gleiwitz was already in the-- see, Kattowitz was on the Polish side-- at one time, not today.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Before the War, Kattowitz was on the Polish side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Gleiwitz was on the German side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we were in Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then they brought in trains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "No, they took us out to the rail station there, to a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And there were trains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But the trains, they were not enclosed trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They were open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They were open trains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They were not cattle cars, they were like freight cars, open, halfway open.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they put us-- they pushed the thing into those cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And the trains started to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And the train moved to Prague.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I remember we passed through Prague towards Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I didn't know where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But we didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We didn't have no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And my lips were black, and my teeth were loose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I remember shaking my teeth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And, and I remember I came to a town which is called Gera, in Germany already, because I saw a sign Gera.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And next to our train there was another train which was enclosed, but the door was slightly open.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And I looked at the people in that train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "They were frightening to look at them, because they were like dead, with their eyes sunken deep.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
